界上最有效，而香港現在至少有4間大學全球排名100名之內，相信高端醫療和高等教育亦可為國家、為香港開創前途，若能配合研究和創科，是可以推動到經濟發展。"},{"pid":"515772e31346e0e5a63acd0739efea34e7f92a2a","tid":2408600,"uid":28155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"講到20年之前冇人去？"},{"pid":"ce679db740a007f55bf93ccd83304d7712bee006","tid":2408600,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80b4f72d94d9f7d1a715b1285ee5789b2c579f3c","tid":2408600,"uid":210712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:35:22.000Z","msg":"唔係點推動旅遊業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0e9bb44f46a666e77c3bd4387836375d45a2fd","tid":2408600,"uid":217383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3daf7da131943cfc6c06e71cfb4e680bbafb5eb","tid":2408600,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T06:36:25.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n香港人就係on9"},{"pid":"54d60d56d4c8ecaeef06df6b6915469607b97336","tid":2408600,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e85354f4e5051fc69a0634be0fe816d2e5bbd40a","tid":2408600,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b834d389197ea038c1c788f4d3efeee0626a22e","tid":2408600,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c996a1c5d3a7fbd54cd536d1f84f7532379477","tid":2408600,"uid":38528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"冇計啦